modName: Beautiful Dark Elf save - WITHOUT EEO
descriptionHtml:
I really wanted to install the Elven Overhaul mod, i think its amazing, but still its not compatible with the ECE.
So i decided to create a nice dark elf character (since im really in love with elf races) without using EEO.
I think finally she came out really nice, feel free to use her face if u want to.
Its a savegame from the start using the Live a New Life mod.

Im going to collect the mods i used.


Mods used:

Live a new life
ApachiiSkyHair (ApachiiSkyHair natural Retexture)
Enhanced Character Edit
SG Female Textures Renewal
SG Female Eyebrows
SG Hair Pack
Better Makeup for SKSE
Calientes Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE
Normalmaps CBBE New
Beautiful eyes
Long EyeLashes



Im really new to the nexus, but im going to check how to make followers, etc, its quite easy for me to catch up with these kinds of things.

I've made a CME version as well, if you want to just load her preset face (slot 8)

Update: Ive uploded my future plans, Freya as a follower or a "real dark elf version" Katarina.
Im still not sure about her name.
But definitely shes going to be an assassin-mage (desctrucion) character.
author: Kumiiho
